Pins the worked examples from doc/proof-cookbook.md.

The cookbook documents the discharge tactics that work for
common SAW-translated goal shapes. If any pattern in the
cookbook breaks (e.g., a theorem rename in
SAWCoreBitvectorsProofs, or a behavioral change in the support
library), proof.lean here fails to elaborate and CI flags it.

Run with `bash test.sh`. Skips cleanly if `lake` is unavailable.
